## Section 2: I Am Rich - How to Create Flutter Apps From Scratch



In 'main.dart'

    void main() {  
	  runApp(  
	    MaterialApp(  
	      home: Scaffold(  
	        backgroundColor: Colors.lightGreen[800],  
		  appBar: AppBar(  
			title: Center(child: Text('새해 복 많이 받으세요!'),),  
